270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025_wetleg_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025_wetleg_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025_wetleg_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Wet-Leg">湿腿</a>宣布了计划在纽约和洛杉矶的两场演出开始他们的新时代。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/wet-leg-announce-their-return-were-so-back-3846997">在本周早些时候分享了他们的回报</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/wet-leg-share-teaser-of-first-new-music-in-three-years-3847341">在三年来的首张新音乐中分享了他们的回报，</a>这是在这之后的。</p><p>现在，乐队为歌迷提供了3月31日在布鲁克林市场酒店的亲密环境和4月8日在洛杉矶的河流中抓住他们的机会。</p><p>他们在Instagram上发表了他们写道：“嘿，邻居没有一段时间了？你为什么不来我们花园的底部？这是我们自己聚会的时候……只是在纽约一个特别的夜晚<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f1fa-1f1f8.png" alt="🇺🇸" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />和洛杉矶<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f1fa-1f1f8.png" alt="🇺🇸" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> 。”</p><p>乐队在3月28日邀请歌迷参加预售，他们可以<a href="https://laylo.com/wetlegband/m/4Mlj5J" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>注册。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DHY3avUtUZa/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-gro