//www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/deadpool-wolverine-review-marvel-3777877"><i>Deadpool＆Wolverine</i></a> ）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/maika-monroe-details-first-time-seeing-nicolas-cage-in-longlegs-makeup-3775626">Maika Monroe</a> （ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/longlegs-review-nicolas-cage-maika-monroe-horror-3774136"><i>Longlegs</i></a> ）领导的。 </p><div id="production-roles" class="prod-listing__details roles"><div class="d-flex flex-xs-row flex-column justify-content-between align-items-start"><p>在2024年秋天，据透露，查理在<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/charli-xcx-brat-summer-timeline-highs-lows-3777880">“小子”夏天</a>的高峰期<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-secretly-filmed-a-movie-in-poland-during-brat-summer-3800475">拍摄了一部名为<em>“埃鲁普贾”</em>的电影</a>。</p><p>在其他地方，她将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-to-headline-and-curate-own-party-girl-festival-at-londons-lido-2025-buy-tickets-3815487">在6月的Lido Festival 2025举行标题并策划一天</a>。 <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Flido-festival-tickets%2Fartist%2F5491324" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问此处</a>的门票。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Charli XCX上的新材料，如果她的粉丝比1975年的粉丝更敬业英国人2024" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/3eCULLsN1Zk?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>查理（Charli）的日子将在她在贝尔法斯特（Belfast）和都柏林（Dublin）以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coachella-2025-lady-gaga-green-day-post-malone-travis-scott-lead-line-up-3814558">Coachella</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-says-she-chappell-roan-and-sabrina-carpenter-headlining-primavera-sound-2025-is-the-holy-trinity-3806307">Primavera Sound的标题上</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-announces-huge-summer-2025-shows-in-belfast-and-dublin-3814479">播放两场户外表演</a>之后。她还排队参加2025年格拉斯顿伯里（Glastonbury）的比赛， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-announced-as-first-parklife-2025-headliner-buy-tickets-3815857">并被确认为明年公园生活的第一个头条新闻</a>。 <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fcharli-xcx-tickets%2Fartist%2F1638380" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处的</a>所有即将举行的演出门票。</p></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcxs-a24-mockumentary-film-the-moment-begins-shooting-as-more-actors-join-cast-3847561">Charli XCX帖子的A24“模拟”电影“时刻”开始拍摄，随着更多演员加入CAST，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
